      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "0.8 - PATHS PANEL"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "All of the paths of interest to SPF/PC may now be specified in a"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "single place. SPF/PC paths may be specified with multiple directories"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "separated by semicolons."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Distinct paths are provided to facilitate shared use on LANS so you"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "can subscribe to a common set of control files while at the same time"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "maintain your own local control files without interfering with others."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The fields on the panel are listed and explained below:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "1 +- Display greater detail on the Paths Panel"
